{
  "chapter": 29,
  "chapter_summary": "第二十九回　莲花开落。剑客行故事继续。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "雷音佛掌",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 18,
      "line_end": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "铁翼神衣",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 20,
      "line_end": 20
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "江南第一家",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 22,
      "line_end": 22
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "一掌震飞鹏，好雄厚的掌力！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 24,
      "line_end": 24
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "展哥哥！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 26,
      "line_end": 26
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "江南第一美人",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 30
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不但认识，看样子人家俩人情感还很好呐……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "一点不错！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我不姓慕容，我姓展！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 84
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "小姐与凌风公子不是亲兄妹吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 86,
      "line_end": 86
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "谁说我与哥哥不是亲兄妹？我姓展——",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 88,
      "line_end": 88
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "江南七侠",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 96,
      "line_end": 96
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "江南七侠",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 100,
      "line_end": 100
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那说不得祥麟就要留驾了！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 150,
      "line_end": 150
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "莫非仗着人多？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "就祥麟一人，也可以留得住贵公子！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 154,
      "line_end": 154
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "来得好！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "有钱的老爷行行好！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 210,
      "line_end": 210
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "可怜叫化苦命的人！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 212,
      "line_end": 212
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你不修今生修来世！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 214,
      "line_end": 214
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "把您那吃不了的残菜剩饭，花不完的金银财宝，也赏给我们穷人几个吧……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 216,
      "line_end": 216
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "原来他还是个花子头。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 220,
      "line_end": 220
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "谁？你说谁是花子头？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 222,
      "line_end": 222
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "喏！就是这一位！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 224,
      "line_end": 224
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "水银寒泉",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 230,
      "line_end": 230
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我们都是没有饭吃的穷朋友！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 258,
      "line_end": 258
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "穷朋友！穷朋友！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 260,
      "line_end": 260
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "一朵莲花开！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 262,
      "line_end": 262
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "莲花，莲花，莲花开又落！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 264,
      "line_end": 264
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "叫化大阵",
